OL,6,FHow to deal with illegal immigration
OL,7,Fis a fundamental dividing line between
OL,8,Fthe two main parties. So first, let's
OL,9,Flook at the numbers.
OL,11,FIn 2022, a record number of people
OL,12,Fmade the dangerous journey across the
OL,13,FEnglish Channel on small boats, with
OL,14,Ftotals hitting nearly 50,000.
OL,16,FThere was a drop in 2023, but so far
OL,17,Fthis year has seen the highest number
OL,18,Fof crossings so far - more than 10,000
OL,19,Fto the end of May.
