OL,3,CPolicy 2024: What to look out for on
OL,4,Cimmigration
OL,6,FNet migration to the UK fell 10% last
OL,7,Fyear after hitting a record high in
OL,8,F2022, but numbers are still huge by
OL,9,Fhistorical standards at 685,000 -
OL,10,Fthat's three times higher than they
OL,11,Fwere in 2019.
OL,13,FWhy? The combination of people fleeing
OL,14,FUkraine and Hong Kong and a rebound in
OL,15,Finternational students post-Covid has
OL,16,Fcoincided with fewer people leaving
OL,17,Fdue to the pandemic and students
OL,18,Fstaying for longer than expected.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G12/22
