OL,3,CPolicy 2024: What to look out for on
OL,4,Cimmigration
OL,6,FDr Madeleine Sumption, Director of the
OL,7,FMigration Observatory at the
OL,8,FUniversity of Oxford said: "This
OL,9,Fperiod of high net migration has now
OL,10,Fpersisted for a while, because it has
OL,11,Fhad several different causes.
OL,12,FInitially, student visas and
OL,13,FUkrainians drove increases in
OL,14,Fmigration, but in 2023 they were
OL,15,Freplaced by health and care work visas
OL,16,Fas the main driver.
OL,18,F"Meanwhile student emigration hasn't
OL,19,Fincreased as much as expected, because
OL,20,Fmore students have been staying on to
OL,21,Fwork."
