OL,3,CPolicy 2024: What to look out for on
OL,4,Cimmigration
OL,6,FRishi Sunak, like his predecessors in
OL,7,Fthe Conservative party, has pledged to
OL,8,Fbring net migration numbers down,
OL,9,Fcommitting to a cap on work and family
OL,10,Fvisas.
OL,12,FTemporary work routes, such as
OL,13,FSeasonal Agricultural Workers, would
OL,14,Fbe exempt from the cap.
OL,16,FThe prime minister has pledged to
OL,17,Fhalve migration, but hasn't put a
OL,18,Ftimeframe on that pledge.
